%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'about'}}
  .content.centered
    #main-title
    .copy.about-text
      %h2 About Us
      %p
        Terra Null, taken from the latin expression Terra Nullius derived from an ancient Roman
        law meaning "Land belonging to no one". With this idea, we at Terra Null Recordings
        try to cultivate an aesthetic that evokes a sense of organic evolution in both art
        and music. A world that belongs to nature rather than man naturally cultivates the
        unfamiliar and strange and is undeterred by the constructs of present human society
        and culture. We try to represent this as best we can through an eclectic collection
        of electronic music and digital artwork that we firmly believe pushes boundaries
        in the best way possible.
        %br
        %br
      %h2 Find Us
      %p
        %a{ href: 'https://www.facebook.com/terranullrecordings', target: '_blank' } Facebook
        %br
        %a{ href: 'https://twitter.com/terranullrecs', target: '_blank' } Twitter
        %br
        %a{ href: 'https://soundcloud.com/terranullrecordings', target: '_blank' } Soundcloud
        %br
        %a{ href: 'http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Fgz_TEywYWZ43BbI9GnkA', target: '_blank' } YouTube
        %br
        %br
      %h2 Send Demos To:
      %p
        TerraNullRecordings [at] gmail [dot] com
        %br
        Requirements:
        %ul#demo-reqs
          %li
            Emails must contain download links to full length tracks (no clips)
          %li
            Mediafire, Sendspace, and wetransfer are preferred
          %li
            Tracks must be 320 kbs mp3s (no wavs or aiffs)
          %li
            Email must contain track name(s), artist name(s), and contact information
          %li
            We prefer one email with many tracks over many emails with only a few tracks

%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'podcasts'}}
  .copy
  %h2.center-text
    COMING SOON

%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'news'}}
  {{#each model}}
  .copy.news-item
    %h2
      {{title}}
    .news-date-text
      {{date_text}}
    %div
      {{markdown content}}
  {{/each}}

  #tertiary-content
    {{outlet}}
  .clear

%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'releases'}}
  #tertiary-content
    {{outlet}}
    .clear

  #release-thumbs-wrapper
    %ul#release-thumbs
      {{#each model}}
      <li>
      {{#linkTo 'release' this class='cool-font release-thumb'}}
      <img {{bindAttr src="cover_thumbnail_src"}} height='200px' class="cover-art"/>
      .release-thumb-copy
        .release-thumb-catalog-number
          {{catalog_number}}
        .release-thumb-title
          {{title}}
      {{/linkTo}}
      .clear
      </li>
      {{/each}}

%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'news-item'}}
  .copy.news-item
    %h2
      {{model.title}}
    %div
      {{markdown model.content}}

%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'release'}}
  {{view Terranullrecordings.ReleaseLightbox data-lightbox=model.title href=model.large_cover_src }}
  .copy.left.release-copy
    .bar
    .release-artist
      {{model.artist}}
    .release-title
      {{model.title}}
    .release-catalog-number
      {{model.catalog_number}}
      %br
      Released {{model.release_date}}
    .bar
    .release-description
      {{markdown model.description}}

%script{type: 'text/x-handlebars', data: {'template-name' => 'release_thumbnail'}}
  <img {{bindAttr src="model.cover_src"}} height='400px' class="cover-art"/>

